#

Fluffy Buttermilk Pancakes with Maple Syrup

25 min
$10
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

glutendairyegg

Dietary Tags:

vegetarian

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Breakfast

Tags:

breakfasteasyquick

Description

Light and airy pancakes drizzled with rich maple syrup, perfect for breakfast or brunch!

Ingredients

  • all-purpose flour: 1 cup
  • buttermilk: 1 cup
  • egg: 1
  • baking powder: 2 tsp
  • sugar: 2 tbsp
  • salt: 1/2 tsp
  • butter (melted): 2 tbsp
  • maple syrup: to taste
